org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl

Class ScriptItemImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.ItemImpl
        • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.ScriptItemImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Item, ScriptItem

    public class ScriptItemImpl
extends ItemImpl
implements ScriptItem
    An implementation of the model object 'Script Item'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Inputs
    • Init Script
    • Update Script
    • Timer
    • Script Engine
    • Commands
    • Write Command Script
